---
alwaysApply: true
---
Use this project as a Flutter WebSerial Gateway on Flutter 3.44.4 / Dart 3.12.2.

Rules:
- Web Serial code belongs only in web-specific data files with conditional imports.
- UI calls serial permission prompts only from direct user gestures like button clicks.
- Normalize every serial payload into domain models before HTTP/WebSocket forwarding.
- Do not hard-code credentials, API tokens, or production URLs.
- Use centralized colors in `lib/core/theme/app_colors.dart` and assets under `assets/`.
- Use English comments in code.
- After code edits run `flutter format .`, `flutter analyze`, and relevant tests.
